# Two-sum: return indices of two numbers that sum to target. -1,-1 if none.
*two_sum(nums, target as i64)
    i is 0
    while i < nums.length
        j is i + 1
        while j < nums.length
            if nums.get(i) + nums.get(j) equals target
                log i
                log j
                return
            j is j + 1
        i is i + 1
    log 0 - 1

*main
    a is vec(2, 7, 11, 15)
    two_sum(a, 9)
